dc_title_s: Hagstrom's map of the world on Mercator's projection
dc_description_s: Hagstrom Company, Inc. North Decimal Degree 80.000000. South Decimal Degree -70.0000. East Decimal Degree 97.50000. West Decimal Degree 82.5000. Mercator projection. International boundaries as of Jan 1, 1949. Standard time zones, air route and ship lane distances are indicated. Ancillary maps: Atlantic Ocean basin and the Pacific Ocean basin. With time comparison chart.
